1. *Važna* je da se zdravo hranimo. (It is important to eat healthy.)
2. On je *važna* osoba u našem društvu. (He is an important person in our society.)
3. *Važno* je da poštujemo druge. (It is important to respect others.)
4. Mi smo *važni* pojedinci u ovoj situaciji. (We are important individuals in this situation.)
5. *Važnost* čitanja ne sme biti zanemarena. (The importance of reading must not be neglected.)